00:23:52.070 --> 00:23:57.539
Optimization is all about getting insight
into your business, understanding, you know,

00:23:57.539 --> 00:24:02.570
metrics and analysis so that you have some
sort of hard data to figure out how to optimize

00:24:02.570 --> 00:24:08.960
