00:25:10.070 --> 00:25:15.950
But what about once they're actually in your
application?

00:25:15.950 --> 00:25:17.139
Then what happens?

00:25:17.139 --> 00:25:22.090
And so Google Analytics is the bit that answers
these questions.

00:25:22.090 --> 00:25:28.109
You can integrate with Google Analytics and
answer questions like how frequently are users

00:25:28.109 --> 00:25:29.109
