00:25:34.639 --> 00:25:37.080
What features are they using or not using?

00:25:37.080 --> 00:25:43.789
Or even more interesting, users that end up
performing in-app purchases, what are their

00:25:43.789 --> 00:25:47.859
behavior patterns, how did they get to the
in-app purchase completion?

00:25:47.859 --> 00:25:49.599
Et cetera.

00:25:49.599 --> 00:25:55.249
If you haven't yet integrated with Google
Analytics, you're missing a pretty good opportunity

00:25:55.249 --> 00:26:00.249
